# Assets Insurance Contractual Regular Contributions Amount

## identifier
de13064

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for the total of all contractual regular contributions. These are the total gross premiums that are accepted through direct debit, have a specific contractual requirement for future on-going premiums, have an expectation of renewal each year (e.g. Yearly Renewable term products) or generally cause a policy to discontinue on cessation of future payment.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Insurance.ContractualRegularContributions.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.09
- period=instant
